617616    2.8815  vmlinux                  vmlinux                  mwait_idle
It looks like tcp in 2.6.22 sends more packets, but frees far less skb than 2.6.24-rc6.
tcp_rcv_established in 2.6.22 is highlighted on cpu utilization.
-yanmin